item.title: eNSP VS WSL 2
item.description: Table Of Contents TLDR Issues Setup Troubleshoot Summary TLDR Conflicts between Hypervisor. Issues I wanted to learn more about Huawei devices, so i chose the Huawei Enterprise Network Simulator Platform eNSP to simulate an enterprise network. So I followed the tutorial from a blog on the internet, but when I tried to run the program, I got the error message “Failed to start device AR1 error code 40.” in eNSP.
